Dear Ms. Smith,

Thank you for reaching out regarding the interest rates on your commercial
loan. As of today, the current interest rate for loan servicing is **5.2%
fixed** for a 10-year term. However, we do offer flexible rate options
depending on your credit profile and collateral.

Would you like me to send a detailed breakdown of different rate options
and their terms?

Best regards,
John Doe
Senior Loan Officer
XYZ Bank

